MBOMBELA &#8211; Couples with their children, moms with babies, friends in support and grandmothers were present. Also noticeable in the audience were a number of fathers of special-needs children, alone. Hannes Viljoen, director and founder of Brain Child Fund understands losing hope of finding help for one&#8217;s children. Judging by the large number of people who attended his talk at Communio Church on Tuesday night, there is a real need for help among parents in the Lowveld.Hannes started Brain Child Fund with his wife Jana to help empower other parents of special-needs children, after walking a difficult road themselves. &#8220;It is a royal flush. Everything you thought you had is gone.